title: Victoria Beckham's New York Fashion Week show: AW17 collection in pictures
text: Victoria Beckham's New York Fashion Week show: AW17 collection in pictures Victoria Beckham's collection has become a regular feature at New York Fashion Week - and she was back today to show her Autumn Winter 2017 designs. Her whole family was there to support her, with husband David and their children Brooklyn, Romeo, Cruz and Harper in the front row.
